---
title: Artichoke Salad with Feta and Golden Potatoes
description: Get transported to Mediterranean with our oh so delicious Artichoke salad.  Oh and did we mention that the artichokes are roasted?!  The crispy outer leaves add the perfect crisp texture to this week night winner!
